description: *** SELLER FUNDED 2/1 BUYDOWN***See attachments!  Updated East Side 3BR/2.5 BA bi-level penthouse featuring 2 roof decks with 1754 sq ft of stunning city views! This light-filled home features central air, soaring ceilings, oversized windows, stained hardwood floors, and lighted ceiling fans in all 3 bedrooms. The main level, perfect for entertaining, boasts a  sprawling open concept living room, dining room, and kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, pendent lighting complimented by recessed lighting. Completing this floor is an updated half bath complete with washer/dryer. Upstairs you’ll find the primary bedroom featuring 2 double closets as well as a spa like ensuite with ceramic counter & double vanity, 2 additional bedrooms with double closets, new carpets, as well as a ceramic tile full bath. Basement storage & one deeded parking spot. A superb location that puts its residents in walking distance to the best of East & West Broadway.
